{"article_id":"QYlEFL7lNttUokiN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"At least 15 people are dead","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"and more than 200 have been reported missing","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"as explosive , wind-whipped wildfires rage through Northern California 's famed wine country ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"forcing fire crews to race","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to get the massive blazes under control .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Sonoma County spokeswoman Maggie Flemings said","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Tuesday afternoon about 200 missing-person reports have been lodged","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"as family members and friends scramble","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"to locate loved ones","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"while wildfires ravage the region .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Flemings said","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"it 's possible that most of those reported missing are safe","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"but ca n't be reached","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"because of the widespread loss of cellphone service and other communications .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Officials are advising people with access to the internet to declare themselves safe on social media or contact the Red Cross .","depth":3},{"id":15,"text":"Cal Fire officials said Tuesday morning","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"17 wildfires in nine counties have already burned more than 115,000 acres in the past 12 hours ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and winds","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"gusting in excess of 50 miles per hour","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"have caused `` extreme rates of spread and volatile burning conditions . ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Fire officials told Fox News","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"there is zero percent containment on all fires .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Some of the largest of the blazes","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"burning","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"were in Napa and Sonoma counties , home to dozens of wineries","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that attract tourists from around the world .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"California Department of Forestry and Fire Protection Chief Ken Pimlott said Tusday","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that 2,000 homes and businesses , in addition to other structures , have been destroyed .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"At least 4,000 personnel are helping to fight the wildfires .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Nine deaths are related to the Tubbs Fire in Santa Rosa County ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"while two have been killed by the Atlas Fire in neighboring Napa County ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"according to fire officials .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Three deaths have also been reported in Mendocino County , and one in Yuba County ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"officials confirmed to Fox News .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Major General David Baldwin said","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"242 soldiers and airmen of the California National Guard are aiding in the response effort in Napa and Sonoma counties .","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"President Trump said Tuesday","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"that the federal government would support California ,","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"and noted","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"he spoke with Gov . Jerry Brown Monday night","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"to `` let him know","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that the federal government will stand with the people of California .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"And we will be there for you in this time of terrible tragedy and need . ''","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Much of the damage was reported in Santa Rosa , a city of 175,000 residents in Sonoma County","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that saw hundreds of homes destroyed by flames so hot","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"they melted the glass off cars .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Former San Francisco Giants pitcher Noah Lowry ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"who now runs an outdoor sporting goods store in Santa Rosa ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"told the Associated Press","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"he was forced to flee along with his wife , two daughters and a son just over 2 weeks old ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"the family only having a few minutes notice .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"`` I ca n't shake hearing people scream in terror","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"as the flames barreled down on us , ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Lowry said .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"In some neighborhoods , half the homes remained untouched","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"while , across the street , cars were charred","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and structures were destroyed .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"One resident","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"wearing an air mask","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"to inspect the damage","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"told KTVU Fox 2","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"she could n't figure out why some people were spared ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and some were n't .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"`` All the houses are untouched , ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"she said of one side of the street .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"`` And I come here","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"and half the neighborhood is torched .","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Why , why why ?","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"Why us ?","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"This is really screwed up .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"It 's heartbreaking .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"It 's really heartbreaking . ''","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Andy Luttringer ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"who lives in Santa Rosa ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"told the SFGate","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"he regretted not grabbing more of his wife ' s artwork .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"His wife died of cancer a few years ago .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"\" I ' m really mad at myself , \"","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"the 62-year-old retired cop told the paper .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"\" I could have grabbed a couple of her pieces .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"The rest of the stuff I couldn ' t care less about . \"","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Hillsides throughout the city were charred from the flames","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"and dotted with smaller fires from ruptured gas lines .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"The fast-racing flames claimed the lives of a Napa couple","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that recently celebrated 75 years of marriage .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Ruby Gibney told KTVU Fox 2","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"her grandparents , Charles","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"- also known as Peach -","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"and Sara Rippey , were unable to escape their home at the Silverado Resort from the Atlas fire","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"and died in the blaze .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Gibney said","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"her grandparent 's home `` was quickly ravaged by the fire ''","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and they were unable to get out in time .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"`` Peach and Sara are immensely loved and missed , ''","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"she told KTVU .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Napa County Sheriff John Robertson said Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"that 100-year-old Charles Rippey and his wife , 98-year-old Sara Rippey , died inside their home .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"`` The only thing worse would have been","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"if one survived","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"without the other , ''","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Gibney said .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Elsewhere in the famed Napa Valley , the Napa Valley Vintners said","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"it does not have verifiable information on winery buildings","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"that burned down","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"or the impact","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"the fires would have on the 2017 harvest .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Workers had picked most grapes for the season","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"before fires broke out .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"Vice President Pence said during a visit to California","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"that the federal government stands ready to provide any and all assistance to the state .","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"California Gov . Jerry Brown has declared a state of emergency in Napa , Sonoma and Yuba counties .","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"In Southern California , more than 5,000 homes were evacuated Monday","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"as fire crews struggled to battle a rapidly growing brush fire .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"The blaze scorched 6,000 acres","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"and destroyed dozens of structures in Orange County ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"and is only five percent contained ,","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"according to Fox 11 Los Angeles .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Plumes of smoke were visible over Disneyland","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"and officials issued air quality warnings for parts of Los Angeles County .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":237,"left":154,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":133,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":132,"right":14,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":123,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":120,"right":122,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":2,"right":121,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":127,"right":130,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":5,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":6,"right":125,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":10,"r